  "obverse": {
    "description": "Grey, green and orange print; multicolour underprint; black serial numbers.\r\n\r\nFront-facing bust of Queen Elizabeth II, wearing the Burmese Ruby Tiara at centre right. Outline map of the Bahamas Islands at centre. Baskets at left. Watermark area at right.\r\n\r\nAscending serial number at lower left. Security thread with country name at left. Bank logo see-through feature at left.",
    "lettering": "THE CENTRAL BANK\r\nOF THE BAHAMAS\r\nTHESE NOTES ARE LEGAL TENDER UNDER THE\r\nCENTRAL BANK OF THE BAHAMAS ACT 2000\r\nFOR THE PAYMENT OF ANY AMOUNT\r\nFIFTY CENTS\r\nSERIES 2001\r\nGovernor\r\n$1/2",
