  "reverse": {
    "description": "Green, yellow and brown print; multicolour underprint.\r\n\r\nSister Sarah in Nassau Market seated, front-facing, surrounded by fruits and fish, people and boats in background. Coat of arms of the Bahamas and bank logo at right. Bananas at lower left. Watermark area at left.",
    "lettering": "THE CENTRAL BANK OF THE BAHAMAS\r\nSISTER SARAH\r\nIN NASSAU MARKET\r\nFIFTY CENTS\r\nDE LA RUE\r\n$1/2\r\nFORWARD UPWARD ONWARD TOGETHER",
